data.text:
To @DHSgov @realDonaldTrump @FBI 
There is officially enough evidence to launch a mass scale investigation into multiple areas involving voter fraud, ballot harvesting, etc. Do something. We expect you to do your jobs. Enough is enough. The people know. We are aware. GET IT DONE

@JacksGhost_ IMO... and I need to research this... ppl were lulled into complacency b/c he won the special by 10 pts, and more resources were poured into OC. And, a source told me one co doing independent ballot harvesting (not paid by Garcia) was scamming their employees.

Same it used to be something that united us...but the loosening of laws related to legal voting have been unraveling for years. There should not be "ballot harvesting" and you should have to show some kind of ID a bill with your name or address, something. https://t.co/k5XFlrmlzC
